  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Gill's Exposition of the Entire Bible",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And the Lord spake unto Aaron,.... Having pointed out to him the duty of his office, he now informs him of the perquisites of it; or having told him what was his work, now what his wages, or what was his service, and now his maintenance: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "behold, I also have given thee the charge of my heave offerings, of all the hallowed things of the children of Israel; such as the heave shoulder and wave breast, and firstfruits, and all other holy things in general, such as were the most holy things; as in Numbers 18:9; and the lighter holy things, as the Jews call them, Numbers 18:11; the charge of these was given to keep for themselves, and for their families: ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "behold, I also have given thee the charge of my heave offerings, of all the hallowed things of the children of Israel; such as the heave shoulder and wave breast, and firstfruits, and all other holy things in general, such as were the most holy things; as in ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Numbers 18:9",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "; and the lighter holy things, as the Jews call them, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Numbers 18:11",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "; the charge of these was given to keep for themselves, and for their families: ",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "unto thee have I given them by reason of the anointing: because of his office as a priest, to which he was consecrated by anointing: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and to thy sons by an ordinance for ever; see Leviticus 7:34. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "and to thy sons by an ordinance for ever; see ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Leviticus 7:34",
            "children": []
          },
          {
